OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early fog quickly clearing
OL,6,Fto leave a bright morning with sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Cloud tending to increase
OL,8,Fthroughout the afternoon, making the
OL,9,Fsunshine hazy with a small risk of the
OL,10,Fodd shower. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather cloudy initially this
OL,14,Fevening with again a small risk of a
OL,15,Fshower. Skies however clearing leaving
OL,16,Fa largely clear and chilly night,
OL,17,Fespecially in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
