OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA bright and sunny start
OL,6,Falthough cloud may bubble up at times
OL,7,Fthroughout the day. A small chance of
OL,8,Fthe odd shower in the north later but
OL,9,Fmost staying dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FStaying dry and settled during the
OL,13,Ffinal days of April with spells of
OL,14,Fsunshine. Feeling warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine, but nights still on the
OL,16,Fchilly side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
